					<div id="mw-content-text" class="mw-body-content"><div class="mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output" lang="en" dir="ltr"><div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">Movement to end constitutional monarchy in Canada</div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt">
</p>
<figure class="mw-halign-right" typeof="mw:File/Thumb"><a href="/wiki/File:CCR_ottawa_chapter_2005.jpg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/49/CCR_ottawa_chapter_2005.jpg" decoding="async" width="300" height="172" class="mw-file-element" data-file-width="300" data-file-height="172" /></a><figcaption>A demonstration on <a href="/wiki/Parliament_Hill" title="Parliament Hill">Parliament Hill</a> by members of <a href="/wiki/Citizens_for_a_Canadian_Republic" title="Citizens for a Canadian Republic">Citizens for a Canadian Republic</a> during the installation ceremony of <a href="/wiki/Governor_General_of_Canada" title="Governor General of Canada">Governor General</a> <a href="/wiki/Micha%C3%ABlle_Jean" title="Michaëlle Jean">Michaëlle Jean</a>, 2005</figcaption></figure>
